thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Barbara

author: Barbara
title: Barbara
text: I am happy with the ease in which I have been able to buy travel insurance. This is the second year as a client and this year, it was necessary to actually speak to someone for clarification of some issue..that was a very positive experience. I have allocated 4 stars..if I allocate 5 stars, it means that I have survived some emergency and fastcover have been of help to me. They make it simple..
